{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9c6c9d6130","title":"管长治揭发胡风在一九二七年就开始了反革命活动","origin":"新华通讯社编《内部参考》1955年6月17日","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"633fe24663","index":0,"year":1955,"month":6,"day":14,"articleId":"9c6c9d6130"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"75307f49a7","type":"title","text":"管长治揭发胡风在一九二七年就开始了反革命活动","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9c6c9d6130"},{"id":"8331a21c9a","type":"paragraph","text":"【云南分社十四日电】管长治揭露胡风在一九二七年就开始了反革命活动。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9c6c9d6130"},{"id":"be69ac2797","type":"paragraph","text":"管长治说：“胡风原是高我一班的小学同学。一九二七年成在武汉入伍时，他在我县(蕲春)国民党县党部当委员，笼络和组织别的委员来与当时的主任委员陈方(共产党员)作对，反对陈的革命主张。”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9c6c9d6130"},{"id":"1d48cbd51e","type":"paragraph","text":"管长治是起义转业军官，曾任二十五集团军总部副参谋长、西南公路运输副司令等伪职。他现在继续回忆他所知道的关于胡风的材料。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9c6c9d6130"},{"id":"2588a7f59c","type":"paragraph","text":"(省政协供给材料)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9c6c9d6130"}],"page":{"id":"702a0f7236","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9c6c9d6130","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}